OL,3,CBritain's largest Muslim festival is
OL,4,Can 'example of unity in divided
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,FBritain's largest Muslim festival will
OL,8,Fgo ahead this weekend and will display
OL,9,Fa "magnificent example of unity" after
OL,10,Fa similar event was forced to end
OL,11,Fearly over an alleged extreme right-
OL,12,Fwing terror threat.
OL,14,FMore than 50,000 Muslims from across
OL,15,Fthe UK and around the world are set to
OL,16,Fattend the Jalsa Salana UK convention
OL,17,Fin Alton, Hampshire this weekend.
OL,26,@qD@COUqD@`O]
