OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784796494
OL,3,CBritain's largest Muslim festival is
OL,4,Can 'example of unity in divided
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,FThe event comes as new polling
OL,8,Fsuggests that 77% of Britons believe
OL,9,Fthe country is more divided than five
OL,10,Fyears ago.
OL,12,FJalsa Salana will begin on Friday,
OL,13,Fless than two weeks after thousands of
OL,14,Fpeople attending the UK Ijtima
OL,15,Fgathering at Shrubland Hall near
OL,16,FIpswich, were forced to leave early on
OL,17,FSunday July 12.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
