PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784796494
OL,3,CBritain's largest Muslim festival is
OL,4,Can 'example of unity in divided
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,FPolice have made 13 arrests and are
OL,8,Fcontinuing to investigate after they
OL,9,Fbecame aware of "a potential serious
OL,10,Fthreat towards the Islamic event" in
OL,11,FSuffolk.
OL,13,FJalsa Salana organisers said they have
OL,14,F"extensive measures in place" to keep
OL,15,Fpeople safe at the convention this
OL,16,Fweekend, which has been held for
OL,17,Faround six decades.
OL,26,@qD@QOUrD@aO]vD@AOUvD@]O]
