PN,38105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784796494
OL,3,CBritain's largest Muslim festival is
OL,4,Can 'example of unity in divided
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,FAhead of the weekend, he said: "At a
OL,8,Ftime when misunderstanding of Islam
OL,9,Fand hostility towards Muslims are
OL,10,Frapidly increasing in many parts of
OL,11,Fthe world, the Jalsa Salana provides
OL,12,Fan outstanding opportunity to present
OL,13,Fthe true teachings of Islam, which are
OL,14,Fof peace, security and goodwill for
OL,15,Fall.
OL,17,F"It is this message of peace that I
OL,18,Fshall deliver to the participants, and
OL,19,Fit is the message that will resonate
OL,20,Fthroughout the Convention.
OL,26,@oD@`OUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
