CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784796494
OL,3,CBritain's largest Muslim festival is
OL,4,Can 'example of unity in divided
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,F"Indeed, the Jalsa Salana is a
OL,8,Fmagnificent example of unity, in which
OL,9,Fpeople from every corner of the world,
OL,10,Fincluding many non-Muslims, come
OL,11,Ftogether in peace and harmony, not
OL,12,Fonly to worship God, but also to
OL,13,Finspire one another to show
OL,14,Fcompassion, love and respect for all
OL,15,Fpeople."
OL,17,FA YouGov poll commissioned by the
OL,18,FAhmadiyya community suggests that more
OL,19,Fthan three quarters of British people
OL,20,Fbelieve the country is more divided
OL,21,Fnow, than it was five years ago.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
