PN,38107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784796494
OL,3,CBritain's largest Muslim festival is
OL,4,Can 'example of unity in divided
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,FThe polling also found that 56% of
OL,8,FBritons believe the positive
OL,9,Fcontributions of British Muslims "are
OL,10,Fnot widely known or recognised" by
OL,11,Fwider British society.
OL,13,FThe results were collated by YouGov
OL,14,Ffrom over 2,000 UK adults in July 2026.
OL,16,FA spokesperson for the community,
OL,17,FKhalil Yousuf, called the findings
OL,18,F"eye opening" and insisted that
OL,19,F"dialogue is the antidote to division".
OL,26,@qD@bOUrD@_O]zD@AOUzD@MO]{D@AOU{D@fO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
