CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784796494
OL,3,CBritain's largest Muslim festival is
OL,4,Can 'example of unity in divided
OL,5,Ccountry'
OL,7,FMr Yousuf said: "Once you meet a
OL,8,FMuslim, I'm sure you'll find we have a
OL,9,Flot more in common than you may have
OL,10,Fpreviously believed."
OL,12,FCaliph Ahmed said it was a cause of
OL,13,F"great grief for all sincere Muslims"
OL,14,Fthat people seek to blame Islam for
OL,15,F"conflict and disorder" in the world.
OL,17,FThe Jalsa Salana UK security team said
OL,18,Fvolunteers are trained to "remain
OL,19,Fvigilant" and have been working
OL,20,Fclosely with the local police.
OL,26,@oD@QOUrD@UO]uD@AOUuD@eO]wD@AOUwD@WO]zD@
